Algorithm:
1.Soil Moisture Sensing Algorithm:
if soil_moisture < moisture_threshold:
    activate_watering_system()
2.Watering Duration Algorithm:
watering_duration = calculate_watering_duration()
activate_watering_system(duration=watering_duration)
3.Weather-based Adjustment Algorithm:
if is_dry_season() and no_rainfall_forecasted():
    adjust_watering_schedule()
4.Blynk Integration Algorithm:
blynk.virtual_write(V1, soil_moisture)
if blynk_button_pressed():
    manual_watering_mode()
